# Summary

cmdOS Mobile Agent extends the AI Execution Operating System into mobile environments.

Traditional mobile systems require users to manage applications.

cmdOS Mobile Agent allows users to express goals and enables AI to execute tasks across devices.

The Mobile Agent creates a continuous AI computing experience across desktop, mobile, and digital environments.
